Submit the approved PIP to the COA Audit Team within the prescribed period;
Conduct the required preliminary activities prior to inventory taking;
Record / document the physical count daily in a standard ICF prescribed in Annex A of COA Circular No. 2020-006 dated January 31, 2020.

We recommended the following courses of action:
Submit the lacking Attendance Sheet for October 1, 2023 and February 5, 2024 LPET;
Submit a written explanation for the splitting of contracts in violation of Section IV B of Annex H of the 2016 Revised IRR of RA 9184;
Prepare Adjusting Journal Entries for the following:
Recognition of the Due to NGAs and Subsidy from National Government Agencies accounts;
Reclassification of LPET expenses from Extraordinary and Miscellaneous Expenses to Training Expenses.

